Class User

java.lang.Object
application.User
public class User extends Object
Represents a user entity in the system.

The User class encapsulates the details of a user, including the username, password, full name, email address, current active role, and a list of all roles assigned to the user. It may also include a mapping of reviewer IDs and a flag indicating if a one-time password (OTP) is active for the user.

Author:
CSE 360 Team 8
